text:
URL bug in "Background - Frequently Asked Questions"
(http://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.2/faq/background.html)
The link "'Powered by Apache' graphic"
(http://httpd.apache.org/docs/apache_pb.gif) routes to a non-existing document
(=> 404 Not Found).

Actually a 301 redirect, which then returns 404. 
 
Now fixed in svn, so that'll percolate through to the site soon - thanks.
